A video Crime Watch shared on their Facebook page shows a criminal jumping over the wall on to a property only to be greeted by two fierce guard dogs, Centurion Rekord reports. The criminal tries to fight off the two bull terriers that started attacking him, but true to their nature, the more the man struggles, the more he aggravates the two dogs. He eventually managed to run to another side of the property with the two dogs strong on his heels. READ MORE: Disturbing photos: SPCA discovers horror abottoir It is unclear where this incident happen, but the date on the video shows 12 January 2017. &#8211; Caxton News Service For more news your way, follow The Citizen on Facebook and Twitter.